{"tid":1165272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方拘8男疑自編自演劫案","createTime":"2019-05-21T16:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T16:23:54.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"849574d1b01792f10648ca503ab5689a9bc1b356","tid":1165272,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕八名男子懷疑他們自編自演一宗兌換店外搶劫案，又涉嫌非法禁錮，懷疑與分贓不均有關。<br />\n<br />\n一名手持黑色袋的男子周一下午報稱，在土瓜灣馬頭涌道一間兌換店外被打劫，損失187萬現金。同日另一名男子報稱被非法禁錮，指因財務糾紛在葵涌被六名男子押上車，警方經調查後，懷疑兩宗案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕八名19至38歲男子，分別涉嫌誤導警務人員、串謀行劫及非法禁錮，其中一人晚上被押回土瓜灣一個單位搜查，會循涉案者的財務狀況、欠債紀錄等方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=348856&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348856%26refer%3D&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=865fa0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348856%26refer%3D&h=1617c438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=348856&amp;refer=</a>"}]}